              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " function is a scalar function in Microsoft SQL Server designed to compute the percentage of electric usage that has been billed over a specified period. This function takes input parameters related to electric usage and billing data, processes them, and returns a single numeric value representing the billed percentage."
